          "reviewBody": "This school has one of the best environment for students accompanied by a lush green surrounding. The teachers are helpful and are always there to help out and look after every child. It is a great place for children to develop social skills, confidence and independence. Teachers have good relationships and a doing an excellent job motivating their students. Students feel happy, safe and are provided a stimulating learning environment. Teachers use all the advanced digital learning practices to sharpen kid’s intellect.",
